  lubezki has also worked with a variety of other major directors , including mike nichols ( the birdcage ) , tim burton ( sleepy hollow ) , michael mann ( ali ) , terrence malick ( the new world , the tree of life , to the wonder , knight of cups ) , martin scorsese ( shine a light , as camera operator under supervision of cinematographer robert richardson ) , and joel and ethan coen ( burn after reading ) .

